; Regression test for issue #729: Output of cleared doesn't align (BZ#729)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/729
;
; The cleared report has a 1-character misalignment: accounts on rows that have
; a last-cleared date are shifted right by 1 character compared to accounts on
; rows without a date. The empty date placeholder uses 9 spaces but format_date()
; produces 10-character dates (e.g., "2000/01/03").

2000/01/01 * Payee One
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

2000/01/02 Payee Two
    Expenses:Books   $25.00
    Assets:Cash

2000/01/03 * Payee Three
    Expenses:Gas     $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test cleared
        $-175.00            $-150.00    00-Jan-03    Assets:Cash
         $175.00             $150.00                 Expenses
          $25.00                   0                   Books
         $100.00             $100.00    00-Jan-01      Food
          $50.00              $50.00    00-Jan-03      Gas
----------------    ----------------    ---------
               0                   0             
end test
